com.jsull.document

Class JsoupExtractor

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jsull.document.JsoupExtractor

  • public abstract class JsoupExtractor
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is the abstract super class of the *Extractor classes. The class provides methods designed to interact with and return portions of the specified web page's DOM.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Josh Sullivan
